Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音乐部期盼已久的入部志愿者终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我叫中野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乐队里是什么位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我是一年二班的中野梓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置的话  吉他稍微会一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和唯一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照  唯前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈～前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～  醒醒啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先弹点什么看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个初学者  弹得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这么快就摆起前辈架子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（齐柏林飞艇(Led Zeppelin)乐队的\N罗伯特·普兰(Robert Plant)与吉米·佩奇(Jimmy Page)）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我强太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  总感觉这气氛好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为我的演奏太差劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉  我弹的果然难以入耳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不  不是因为这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还差得远呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你还要装到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想再听一次唯前辈的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出的时候腰扭到了  下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了你  一边凉快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你是打算要入部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了各位在新生欢迎会演出上的演奏  我十分感动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好闪好耀眼  无法直视她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的入部申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始请多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好有活力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我很早就期待着放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  在音乐室做这种事情没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一杯奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是顾问山中佐和子  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是个美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似这孩子挺适合猫耳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用点心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的看起来也好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有新入部员  真是春天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天到了就能找到男友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操心  多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是轻音部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说她们在试探我的自觉性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和你个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  人家想安静地喝茶嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也该注意下你的语气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  那个老师稍微有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃块蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟午茶时间是我们的招牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  爆发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全感受不到大家的干劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…你看新生欢迎会才刚刚结束不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得把音乐室占为己有也是不对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶具也应该全部撤掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你就饶了我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么老师来求情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  总之先冷静下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样怎么能让我冷静啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子～乖孩子～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做怎么可能稳住她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稳住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱了方寸真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦  我们完全没放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓说的也有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要再拿出点干劲来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前给大家添了麻烦  真是不想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫没有动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们现在正准备去练习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不吃蛋糕就没力气啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也尝尝看吧  很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:48.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：果然蓬头乱发才是唯的萌点啊XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说「可惜」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（好吃（おいしい）与可惜（おしい）一音之差）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不合你的口味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今开始音乐室就没有午茶时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  老师就得好好做个老师的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  在好好练习吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这不是在吃吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  死在这里也满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么最后没把茶具都撤掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我觉得什么都否定掉是不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓是从什么时候开始弹吉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…差不多是小学四年级开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为双亲在搞爵士乐队的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全不是初学者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯前辈开始弹吉他的契机是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来  觉得轻音乐是简单的音乐这种话说不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:39.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：口胡！明明新欢Live时都在台上公布于众了XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～总之有新部员加入真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙混过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我给小梓带礼物来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗙嗙嗙嗙～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是猫耳咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个要怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦  这就像轻音部的仪式一类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的仪式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个害羞的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的啊  前辈们也觉得害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不愧是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  难道是我比较奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  接下来该轮到小梓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不会看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到轻音部！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓真可爱啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说声喵试试  喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外号「梓喵」就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来换这件！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫耳女仆！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝对不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿很合身的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说被玩弄的对象从我变成了梓这点让人轻松不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这寂寞感…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才起在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没练习就累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我有东西忘在音乐室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡…胡子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难受哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近有家好吃的冷饮店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈请客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  回答要用「喵」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜咕噜咕噜咕噜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被驯服中！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋粘到嘴上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？ 你觉得能适应轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这股悠哉悠哉的气氛有点那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系！马上就会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我并不想习惯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（紧急会议中！不得入内！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急会议是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为既然有新部员进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成天到晚无所事事也不是个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去梓很可能会退部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要梓喵走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  只好去找找她的弱点…疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该立定个像样子的活动计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得有理呢  那就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来给梓开个欢迎会好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  梓喵你也吃点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓你尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢鲷鱼烧啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你往哪里扔呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪前辈很有实力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么会加入这么不上进的社团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  澪前辈有没有在外面组乐队？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确跑外场也挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～你觉得说这种话好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌…貌似被抓到弱点了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔女郎也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要准备不少东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真一如既往地强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不想穿的话  那就我们穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去哪里好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物园怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉也不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是个好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那下次我们就去温泉咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始一定要好好练习了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的一定的一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！虽然各位可能已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我可没忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们要开始练习了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！既然现在唯和梓都是吉他手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曲子的领域也可以扩展开来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁来做主音吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那自然是由前辈来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我！ 我来做！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这自信从哪儿来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是听过你们的演奏再决定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就从我开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（柯特·科本(Kurt Cobain)  著名乐队涅磐(Nirvana)主唱）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓她很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来换唯你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我自重…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵！求求你教我弹吉他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,态度变得太快了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里变闷音的话会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有刚才的乐节用颤音弹奏的话会更合适
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（乐节（phrase）：在结构上大于动机的部分，\N是在曲调和节奏组织上较为独立的片段）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷音？颤音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（揉弦（Vibration）：手指按某音时用一种方式运动，\N使发音围绕某音的频率细微变化，即颤音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她这样也熬过一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷音和颤音都不知道那她怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？闷音弹得好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个就是闷音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓闷音  就是轻按琴弦阻止其发音的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:23.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小佐和笔记）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她就是那种买来游戏也不会看说明书的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看差不多可以上宫廷奶茶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天我们要练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先休息一小会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～明天再来努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是小梓专用的杯子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要废了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去就要废了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别只挂在轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的乐队也来参与一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有其它出色的乐队…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何乐队都比轻音部强上千百倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近梓喵都不怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许以后也不来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近怎么都不来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我们可是天天练习来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是来说要退部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个万万不可啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂为什么要进轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂新生欢迎会的演奏为什么会让我那么感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为在一起一段时间后就能理解才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我还是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！那我们来为梓演奏一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当为了让她想起当初那个感觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯前辈连基本的音乐用语都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈的鼓点也太过急促
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要四人合起来演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就会变成这么好的曲子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你不是问我为什么不去外面组乐队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是最喜欢和现在的成员在一起演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会有这样出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  和我们一起演奏吧  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！我果然还是想和前辈们在一起演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想虽然今后还是会有喝茶吃点心等懒懒散散的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这应该也是必要的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我燃尽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的一周我都不想演奏了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～戴个猫耳来看看～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你啦  你戴完我就努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊萌啊～啾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是暑假  但真够辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研修什么的都撞在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部要搞合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问问老师你要不要来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…一副麻烦死了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能好好练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷心菜真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:09.71,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#10　　又是合宿!


